ro þ 2re þz RS-MSPs created by destroying the
conflicting 2-cycles. By Lemma 8, the number of
RS-MSPs destroying conflicting 2-cycles is not greater
than s3r þ sar . Thus, s3r þ sar  ro þ 2re þz. The
lemma holds. tu
